casebody.data:
Kurt E. HUEBERT et al. v. ST. PAUL FIRE & MARINE INSURANCE COMPANY, a Corporation. No. 4924. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. June 22, 1954. J. Rodney Stone, Newton, Kan., for appellants. Fleeson, Gooing, Coulson & Kitch, Wichita, Kan., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Chief Judge, and BRATTON and HUXMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed for failure diligently to prosecute.
